{"tid":1687140,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一名消防員周四晚旺角示威活動現場被捕","createTime":"2019-11-01T15:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T17:08:27.000Z","uid":212626,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"933605788446e3de3e4404ff849b7ca2884fe914","tid":1687140,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:25:27.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】一名消防員周四晚在旺角示威活動現場被警方拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n一批示威者周四晚，趁831太子站事件兩個月，在太子和旺角一帶集結，並且堵路和縱火，防暴警察出動驅散。<br />\n<br />\n消防處證實一名屬員當晚在旺角區涉嫌干犯刑事案件，現正接受警方調查，指由於相關執法部門已經展開調查，消防處沒有其他資料補充。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=368407\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D368407&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8DyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=8eaf6b2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D368407&h=08476b04\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=368407</a>"},{"pid":"333e664ee2156d805fa12d28c48b3e8b08ed8657","tid":1687140,"uid":308414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:26:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c7d81a33d562340c2e5fd994f093657dff2b8c9","tid":1687140,"uid":167548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:26:12.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a018625073975b51fcfb1f190e81bb765d3c085a","tid":1687140,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:26:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=